{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"工具链","page":{"layout":"document","title":"quickstart","description":"- Github Template: eunomia-bpf/eunomia-template - example bpf programs: examples/bpftools - tutorial: eunomia-bpf/bpf-developer-tutorial","bodyHtml":"<ul>\n<li>Github Template: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-template\">eunomia-bpf/eunomia-template</a></li>\n<li>example bpf programs: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/blob/master/examples/bpftools\">examples/bpftools</a></li>\n<li>tutorial: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/bpf-developer-tutorial\">eunomia-bpf/bpf-developer-tutorial</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can get pre-compiled eBPF programs running from GitHub Pages URLs or an OCI registry in <code>1</code> line of bash:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># download the latest release (aka.pw/bpf-ecli redirects to the current GitHub release asset)</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">$</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> wget</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://aka.pw/bpf-ecli</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -O</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> &#x26;&#x26; </span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">chmod</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> +x</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">$</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://eunomia-bpf.github.io/eunomia-bpf/sigsnoop/package.json</span><span style=\"color:#768390\"> # historical GitHub Pages workflow, kept for compatibility</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">$</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ghcr.io/eunomia-bpf/execve:latest</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>The legacy remote HTTP mode (<code>ecli client</code> / <code>ecli-server</code>) has been removed from the main branch and archived on <code>archive/ecli-remote-http</code>.</p>","headings":[],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/quickstart.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-08T04:58:07.000Z","createdAt":"2023-08-10T12:54:12.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"},{"name":"oluceps","email":"ospp@oluceps.uk"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"在线体验网站","description":"可使用 bolipi 提供的在线体验服务，在线编译，在线运行、在线获取可视化结果：https://bolipi.com/ebpf/home/online","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/online/"},"next":{"title":"build on android aarch64","description":"Android上build需要先Installing Debian on Android in Termux","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc"